A Slovenian truck that probably turned from the parking lane blocking the passage to the bus without using the blinkers.
His driver tried in a quick maneuver to avoid it, however, he collided with the right front.
Jan<0xC4><0x8D>ura denies that the two sites that are reserved for the rest of the hostess were sold.
"These sites cannot be booked for long-distance connections, they are blocked."
