The agency will not wait for the verdict of the trial on the compensation of the family of the girl but expects the financial expenses also on the part of the culprit.
Reform of the law?
No, for now.
The reform of the law could bring greater precision on the movement of the hostess on the bus in which for a year thirty expert members of a group of the Ministry of Transport are working.
