According to statistics, between 30% and 75% of motorists reported more than once for drunk driving again take the car.
The alcoholock would avoid this because it is a system connected to the vehicle that measures the rate of alcohol in exhaled air and prevents starting the car if the driver does not blow abtes; or when a concentration of alcohol is detected is higher than that allowed.
