And there is no lack of even the realities that offer an ideal training, consultation and assistance service for small and medium-sized companies, in which business prospects could be opened.
Open Office consists of five main modules: Writer, for video writing the corresponding of Word; Calc, is the worksheet that replaces Excel; Impress, for the presentation of Powerpoint; Dbase, comes in the case of the known Access is the program that allows to work in the data base; and finally Draw the graphical module.
